ChunkText: change of education or degree level a change of education level means you will continue your studies at umbc, but are starting a new degree program. this could be english students beginning a degree program, bachelors degree students transitioning to masters, or masters students transitioning to phds.
ContextAfter: this could also be starting a second degree at umbc at the same degree level. since you will remain at umbc in this situation to start your new degree program, the process to adjust your I-20 for this new program is relatively simple.
